children.description: Given the user is on the mac-center.com platform using "chrome"
Johan open main
Johan opens the browser at https://mac-center.com/

When adds the following items to the cart
| Iphone 13 |
| Macbook pro |
| Airpods |
Johan search item
Johan clicks on the search box
Johan enters 'Iphone 13',ENTER into the search box
Johan add item to cart
Johan clicks on [[ChromeDriver: chrome on windows (91f20c51ddf0d4c40dd8e5487a4f709f)] -> xpath: //button[@data-available = 'Agregar al carrito']]
Johan clicks on the close button
Johan search item
Johan clicks on the search box

Johan clicks on the close button

Johan add item to cart
Johan clicks on [[ChromeDriver: chrome on windows (91f20c51ddf0d4c40dd8e5487a4f709f)] -> xpath: //button[@data-available = 'Agregar al carrito']]
Johan clicks on the close button
And goes to the cart
Johan open cart
Johan clicks on the cart link button
Johan clicks on the go to the cart button
Johan confirm cart
Johan clicks on the confirm purchase button
And confirms their credentials using bbva payment method

Johan enters '12490349236' into the id field
Johan enters 'Madeline' into the name field

Johan continue to payment

Johan clicks on continue payment button
Johan select bbva option
Johan clicks on continue BBVA payment option
Johan fill out bbva form
Johan enters '4413505798784009' into the card number input
Johan enters 'Madeline Kuhn' into the card name input
Johan selects #value in the card month box
Johan selects #value in the card year box
Johan enters '115' into the CCV input
Johan selects #value in the card installment box
Johan selects #value in the id type box
Johan enters '12490349236' into the id type options
Johan clicks on the terms and conditions check box
Then should see its information in the card
Then card number should be a string containing '4413'
Then card number should be a string containing '4009'
And should be able to confirm the payment
Then pay button enabled should be (true)
